msgstr "Akkaawuntiin kee {source} irraa as fidame. Achitti haqtee hanga fixtutti, ergaawwan fi beeksisawwan sarvara lamaaniyyuu ga'uu danda'u, qabeenyi kee tokko tokko sarvaraa durii irraa tajaajilamu itti fufa, fi hordoftonni si argachuu dhaaf daqiiqaawwan muraasa fudhachuu danda'u."
